table_caption: Changes in headache frequency, migraine frequency, and ASC-12 scores. Change in headache and migraine frequency compares weeks 5–8 after the first erenumab treatment to the 4-week pre-treatment period. Change in ASC-12 scores compares those obtained during the research visit at 8 weeks after the first erenumab treatment to those collected just before the first treatment. ASC-12 = Allodynia Symptom Checklist 12
